    <tr>
      <td colspan="2"><span class="style1">During the Safety Orientation the new employee will complete the &quot;Safety and Accident Prevention Test&quot;. Grade this with them and explain any of the questions they missed so they understand the correct answer. Record their grade on the first page of the Orientation Booklet in the Employee File Index along with the other Safety Orientation documents. When the orientation is complete the Employee file index will look like this. </span></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width="236"><p align="left">Notice that dates are used rather that checkmarks. Jack Hammer received his orientation on 10-02. We know this because the orientation date is the one used to fill in the file index.</p>
